name: Net Tango
tag_list: web-design, web-development, web-applications, database-solutions, mobile-application-development, seo, social-media-integration, online-marketing-services
overview:
Net Tango, headquartered in Louisville, Kentucky, develops interactive websites, web applications, database solutions, and mobile applications for clients of all sizes, ranging from individual entrepreneurs to Fortune 100 companies. Net Tango also offers social media integration, SEO, and online marketing services.

Net Tango knows how to leverage technology to achieve business goals. As business professionals, they understand a company’s needs for practical, cost-effective technology solutions to generate revenue, reduce costs, facilitate communication and collaboration, and to streamline or improve business processes.
